headline: Welltower: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The Toledo, Ohio-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $1.03 billion, or $1.45 per share, in the period. The average estimate of four analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $1.44 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
